OL,3,CGalloway National Park: What were the
OL,4,Carguments for and against?
OL,6,FRepresenting Border's Matty Sutton has
OL,7,Fbeen speaking to people in communities
OL,8,Facross Galloway, hearing why they
OL,9,Floved...or loathed the idea of a
OL,10,Fnational park.
OL,12,FThe Scottish Government agency
OL,13,FNatureScot has been consulting on
OL,14,Fwhether Galloway should be designated
OL,15,FScotland's third national park.
OL,17,FThe Scottish Government announced on
OL,18,F29 May 2025 that the plans had been
OL,19,Fscrapped.
