OL,3,CGalloway National Park: What were the
OL,4,Carguments for and against?
OL,6,FSpeaking in Holyrood this afternoon
OL,7,F(29 May 2025), Rural Affairs Secretary
OL,8,FMairi Gougeon MSP said the government
OL,9,Fhad "made the decision not to proceed
OL,10,Fwith the designation of a new national
OL,11,Fpark for Galloway and Ayrshire".
OL,13,FShe said the government had "weighed
OL,14,Fup the arguments for and against" the
OL,15,Fproposal, adding that the public
OL,16,Fconsultation had seen 54% of
OL,17,Frespondents outline their opposition,
OL,18,Fwhile 42% were in favour.
OL,20,FHere are some of the arguments from
OL,21,Fthose on both sides of the debate.
