OL,3,CGalloway National Park: What were the
OL,4,Carguments for and against?
OL,6,FSusan Dixon runs self-catering holiday
OL,7,Faccommodation at Carsethorn.
OL,9,F"I think it would bring more visitors
OL,10,Fto the area, which is really needed,"
OL,11,Fshe said.
OL,13,F"It's a lovely area all year round.
OL,14,FWhen I did B&B people used to say I've
OL,15,Fnever visited this corner of Scotland
OL,16,Fbefore, they've all been to the
OL,17,FHighlands and Islands and Edinburgh
OL,18,Fand Stirling, but they'd not been here
OL,19,Fand they were really pleasantly
OL,20,Fsurprised at how beautiful it was and
OL,21,Fthey wanted to come back."
