OL,3,CGalloway National Park: What were the
OL,4,Carguments for and against?
OL,6,FSteve Norris is the former editor of
OL,7,Fthe Galloway Gazette and an SNP
OL,8,Fcampaigner.
OL,10,F"I've seen over the decades a slow and
OL,11,Fperceptible decline in Galloway and
OL,12,Fit's ongoing," he said.
OL,14,F"School rolls are falling, and we need
OL,15,Fto do something to turn around our
OL,16,Feconomy. The number of pubs,
OL,17,Fhospitality businesses, restaurants
OL,18,Fand so on that have closed down in
OL,19,FGalloway in the last 30 or 40 years
OL,20,Fthere's dozens, perhaps hundreds of
OL,21,Fthem.
