OL,3,CGalloway National Park: What were the
OL,4,Carguments for and against?
OL,6,F"Wee villages are dying on their feet,
OL,7,Fschools are closing and a Galloway
OL,8,Fnational park to me is a way, over a
OL,9,Ffew years, to begin to rebuild the
OL,10,Feconomic and social fabric of our
OL,11,Farea."
OL,13,FDenise Brownlee co-founded the No
OL,14,FGalloway National Park campaign group.
