OL,3,CGalloway National Park: What were the
OL,4,Carguments for and against?
OL,6,F"My main concern when I started all of
OL,7,Fthis off was that I'd lived and worked
OL,8,Fin a national park in the past, and I
OL,9,Fdidn't want to see the devastation and
OL,10,Fdestruction that I saw on a daily
OL,11,Fbasis when I was a ranger, I didn't
OL,12,Fwant that to happen here," she
OL,13,Fexplained.
OL,15,F"And I used to, when I was out and
OL,16,Fabout up in Loch Lomond, be on my
OL,17,Ftravels just doing what rangers would
OL,18,Fdo, and the amount of human waste was
OL,19,Fheartbreaking and I didn't want to see
OL,20,Fthat here."
