OL,3,CGalloway National Park: What were the
OL,4,Carguments for and against?
OL,6,F"Yes, a national park could do those
OL,7,Fthings, but my fear, and many others
OL,8,Ffear in the region, not just farmers,
OL,9,Fis that this stops businesses, because
OL,10,Fthey hear it's a national park and
OL,11,Fthey hear and it's nothing but hurdles
OL,12,Fand constraints, rather than a place
OL,13,Fthat was welcoming and open to
OL,14,Fbusiness."
